{"tid":2151031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"顧委會倡港台滙報重大投訴  工會斥管過界","createTime":"2020-08-11T07:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T07:51:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"07aff6b2ccf7de2e11b9e78fc7a1e882ed26d88c","tid":2151031,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:51:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/FHRBTVTEPFTBV2I5TDBXWFYAJY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FFHRBTVTEPFTBV2I5TDBXWFYAJY%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=238dff24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FFHRBTVTEPFTBV2I5TDBXWFYAJY%2F&h=c25af333\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/FHRBTVTEPFTBV2I5TDBXWFYAJY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n顧委會倡港台滙報重大投訴 <br />\n工會斥管過界<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/88DwWh8TRmqowiE1Ccq4qtAdjRg=/640x468/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GAAB4NXYNIT234FL63TEBARGRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F88DwWh8TRmqowiE1Ccq4qtAdjRg%3D%2F640x468%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGAAB4NXYNIT234FL63TEBARGRE.jpg&h=16102fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳建強（左）稱顧委會不會介入港台日常運作。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】被指是「太上皇」的港台顧問委員會，早前成立投訴工作小組，昨早舉行會議。顧委會主席陳建強會後會見傳媒時表示，顧委會首次建議港台應向委員會交代有關重大及社會關注的投訴。他強調並非要處理投訴，又重申顧委會不會介入港台日常運作，但有責任提醒港台要嚴肅、迅速、審慎處理每宗投訴。他指港台今年接獲廣管局兩宗警告，反映港台投訴機制有很大改善空間，促港台反思，「絕對唔可以怠慢或者故步自封」。<br />\n<br />\n顧委會投訴工作小組昨早舉行會議，八名顧委會成員和廣播處長梁家榮等出席。主席陳建強會後稱，首次建議港台如有重大事宜或社會關注議題，應盡快告知顧委會。被問到何。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n陳指今年港台接獲廣管局兩宗警告，其中一宗是「嚴重警告」，作為總編輯的廣播。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/y-cfw_BeugRTEluwbIC9R4KdUH0=/639x417/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QGGIYHIAERVBJ7FKBBYKUCZLVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fy-cfw_BeugRTEluwbIC9R4KdUH0%3D%2F639x417%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQGGIYHIAERVBJ7FKBBYKUCZLVY.jpg&h=f6c89913&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港台節目《頭條新聞》的「驚方訊息」環節，早前被警方投訴。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳建強：要宣傳一國兩制<br />\n<br />\n陳又指處長應帶領港台員工理解《香港電台約章》精神和目的，並從節目裏。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於建制派立法會議員何君堯早前投訴港台節目《鏗鏘集》一事，他稱。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n香港電台回應表示，按《香港電台約章》，顧委會就港台的服務向處長。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港台節目製作人員工會主席趙善恩表示，港台的日常運作有規有序，一直。。。。。。。。"}]}